(187, 2, '2013-01-24 10:36:56', '2013-01-24 10:36:56', '<p>All LA charter high school students with unique needs and their parents are invited to explore post-secondary options and community resources! Granada Hills Charter High School in partnership with Birmingham Community Charter High School is hosting an evening focused on transition.\nParents and students with disabilities are invited to explore transition resources through a highly interactive experience, which is designed to introduce parents and students to post-secondary options and adult community resources.  Parents and students will have opportunity to speak individually with representatives from the Disabilities Offices and Outreach Departments from the local Community Colleges, Cal State Northridge, and Career Tech Ed Centers.  In addition, representatives from community programs will provide intensive transition assistance with academic, independent living and social skills to students with disabilities.  Lastly, community programs, that assist students with ASD, ADHD, and other Learning challenges, will offer opportunities for students to participate in career development and life skills curriculum.\n- <a href="http://www.ccsa.org/blog/members/Reach_for_success_event_flyer_2013.pdf">See the flyer for event location and additional information.</a></p>\n', 'February 28: Reach For Success: An Evening of Transition for Students with Disabilities', 'All LA charter high school students with unique needs and their parents are invited to explore post-secondary options and community resources at this free event! Granada Hills Charter High School in partnership with Birmingham Community Charter High School is hosting an evening focused on transition.\n', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'february_28_reach_for_success_an_evening_of_transition_for_student_with_disabilities', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '', 0, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/february_28_reach_for_success_an_evening_of_transition_for_student_with_disabilities/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(188, 2, '2013-02-01 16:39:28', '2013-02-01 16:39:28', '<p>El hijo de Norma Colado participó en un concurso de NASA y también viajo a Turquia, gracias a su escuela chárter -- Magnolia Science Academy #3 en Carson, CA. "Mi hijo está practicando lo que realmente le gusta," dice Norma, uno de cientos de padres que <a href="/2012/11/victoria-para-los-padres---lausd-rechaza-resolucion-que-limitaria-opciones-para-padres.html">marcharon en frente del distrito escolar de Los Angeles a favor de las escuelas chárter en noviembre de 2012.</a></p>\n\n<div class="video-container"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/bJRMa2yULZ8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n', 'VIDEO: "Las Escuelas Chárter Dan Oportunidades"', 'El hijo de Norma Colado participó en un concurso de NASA y también viajo a Turquia, gracias a su escuela chárter -- Magnolia Science Academy #3 en Carson, CA.\n', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'video_las_escuelas_charter_dan_oportunidades', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '', 0, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/video_las_escuelas_charter_dan_oportunidades/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(189, 2, '2013-02-01 17:13:58', '2013-02-01 17:13:58', '<p>Cuando su hijo entró a la escuela, no pudo leer, pero gracias a Animo Jefferson, una escuela chárter en Los Angeles, CA, recibió la ayuda que necesitaba dice Maria Tostado. Quiere que más niños de educación especial tengan esta oportunidad. Por eso, se juntó con cientos de padres que <a href="/2012/11/victoria-para-los-padres---lausd-rechaza-resolucion-que-limitaria-opciones-para-padres.html">marcharon en frente del distrito escolar de Los Angeles a favor de las escuelas chárter en noviembre de 2012. </a></p>\n\n<div class="video-container"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/IzM_elTMz1Y" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n', 'VIDEO: "Necesitamos más escuelas chárter"', 'Maria Tostado de Animo Jefferson en Los Angeles dice que su escuela le ayudó mucho a su hijo y quiere que más estudiantes con necesidades especiales tengan esta oportunidad.\n', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'video_necesitamos_mas_escuelas_charter', '', '', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '2016-01-13 04:22:20', '', 0, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/video_necesitamos_mas_escuelas_charter/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
