(437, 1, '2015-12-09 07:31:29', '2015-12-09 07:31:29', 'The CCSA Families vision is that all California children and their families have great charter schools to choose from. We unite charter school families and teachers across California into a powerful voice for excellent schools. We help families, teachers, and alumni become leaders in their communities.\r\n\r\n<strong>We Turn Lightning Into Electricity</strong>\r\nThe power we harness is like electricity. We are building an electrical grid of charter school champions across the state. Our parent, teacher, and alumni leaders and teams can mobilize because they are organized.', 'Our Vision', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '436-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-09 07:31:29', '2015-12-09 07:31:29', '', 436, 'http://192.168.20.50/wp/436-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
