(1221, 10, '2016-01-19 18:55:59', '2016-01-19 18:55:59', '<p>More than 500 people, including many charter school parents and students, represented the charter school movement at CCSA\'s annual Advocacy Day in Sacramento this week. In one-on-one meetings with legislators, families shared their experiences at charter school and urged legislators to support bills that will help charters thrive, and to oppose efforts to rob charters of their autonomy. Congratulations and thank you to the many charter families who shared their voices inside the halls of the Capitol!</p>\n\n<p><strong><em>https://www.ccsa.org/cgi-bin/mt/mt.cgi?__mode=view&amp;&#95;type=asset&amp;id=5673&amp;blog&#95;id=10</em></strong></p>\n', 'Families Hit the Capitol at CCSA Advocacy Day', 'Charter school parents and students represented the charter school movement at CCSA\'s annual Advocacy Day in Sacramento.\r\n', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '362-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 18:55:59', '2016-01-19 18:55:59', '', 362, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/362-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
