(1413, 10, '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '<p>Legislators in Sacramento are being pressured to pass new laws that will hinder charter school independence and effectiveness. So far, they\'ve only heard from special interests. Now they need to hear from you. Please take a minute to <a href="https://www.votervoice.net/CCSA/campaigns/39808/respond?mkt_tok=3RkMMJWWfF9wsRols6rKZKXonjHpfsX56%2BkvWKSylMI%2F0ER3fOvrPUfGjI4FTsNjI%2BSLDwEYGJlv6SgFTrfMMaNvzbgIXxI%3D">sign this petition opposing Assembly Bill 787</a>, which would take away the independence of charter schools across California.</p>\n\n<p>Stay tuned in the coming weeks and watch for emails inviting you to share your voice, stand up for charter schools, and tell lawmakers not to create new laws that get in the way of charter school success.</p>\n', 'Help Fight Anti-Charter Legislation!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'help-fight-anti-charter-legislation', '', '', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '', 0, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/?p=1413', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1414, 10, '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '<p>Legislators in Sacramento are being pressured to pass new laws that will hinder charter school independence and effectiveness. So far, they\'ve only heard from special interests. Now they need to hear from you. Please take a minute to <a href="https://www.votervoice.net/CCSA/campaigns/39808/respond?mkt_tok=3RkMMJWWfF9wsRols6rKZKXonjHpfsX56%2BkvWKSylMI%2F0ER3fOvrPUfGjI4FTsNjI%2BSLDwEYGJlv6SgFTrfMMaNvzbgIXxI%3D">sign this petition opposing Assembly Bill 787</a>, which would take away the independence of charter schools across California.</p>\n\n<p>Stay tuned in the coming weeks and watch for emails inviting you to share your voice, stand up for charter schools, and tell lawmakers not to create new laws that get in the way of charter school success.</p>\n', 'Help Fight Anti-Charter Legislation!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1413-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '2016-01-20 20:21:55', '', 1413, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/1413-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1415, 10, '2016-01-20 20:22:41', '2016-01-20 20:22:41', '<p>Legisladores en Sacramento están recibiendo presión para aprobar nuevas leyes que van a impedir la independencia y eficacia de las escuelas chárter. Hasta ahora, solo han escuchado opiniones de los grupos de interés especial. Ahora tienen que escuchar de usted. Por favor tome un minuto para <a href="https://www.votervoice.net/CCSA/campaigns/39808/respond?mkt_tok=3RkMMJWWfF9wsRols6rKZKXonjHpfsX56%2BkvWKSylMI%2F0ER3fOvrPUfGjI4FTsNjI%2BSLDwEYGJlv6SgFTrfMMaNvzbgIXxI%3D">firmar esta petición en oposición al Proyecto de Ley de la Asamblea 787</a>, lo cual impediría la independencia de las escuelas chárter en todo California.</p>\n\n<p>Manténgase atento en las próximas semanas y busque correos electrónicos que le invitan a compartir su voz, defender las escuelas chárter y decirles a los legisladores que no creen nuevas leyes que impidan el éxito de las escuelas chárter.</p>\n', 'Ayude en luchar contra la legislación antichárter', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'ayude-en-luchar-contra-la-legislacion-anticharter', '', '', '2016-01-20 20:22:41', '2016-01-20 20:22:41', '', 0, 'http://dev.ccsafamilies.org/?p=1415&#038;lang=es', 0, 'post', '', 0) ;
